spec_data.Name: ghc-blaze-builder-conduit
spec_data.Description:
Convert a stream of blaze-builder Builders into a stream of ByteStrings.
Adapted from blaze-builder-enumerator.  The functions provided work in
any monad built on top of IO or ST.
